CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 7, 1964, pg. 3 reads: "Discussion - Charles C. Cooper, chairmen of the Men's Committee of the Health-O-Rama Planning Committee to hold the health program in April at the Savoy Ballroom on Centre Ave., is shown in a discussion with (left to right, standing) John C. Waters, Stephen W. Lenhardt, Taylor Thompson, co-chairman; Edmond McKenzie and Dan Laley. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Charles C. Cooper holding Health-O-Rama brochure, discussing Health-O-Rama plans with, from left: John C. Waters, Stephen W. Lenhardt, Taylor Thompson, Edmond McKenzie and Dan Laley, in interior with television and landscape painting
